      1545,
      1078,
      2043
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} f'(x) = 0 \\Leftrightarrow 2 \\cos 2x + \\sqrt{2} = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\cos 2x = -\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} = \\cos \\frac{3\\pi}{4} \\\\ \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} 2x = \\frac{3\\pi}{4} + k2\\pi \\\\ 2x = -\\frac{3\\pi}{4} + k2\\pi \\end{cases} \\quad (k \\in \\mathbb{Z}) \\\\ \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x = \\frac{3\\pi}{8} + k\\pi \\\\ x = -\\frac{3\\pi}{8} + k\\pi \\end{cases} \\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      213,
      2052,
      1412,
      2147
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Trên đoạn $\\left[\\frac{\\pi}{3}; \\pi\\right]$: $\\frac{\\pi}{3} \\leq \\frac{3\\pi}{8} + k\\pi \\leq \\pi \\Leftrightarrow -\\frac{1}{24} \\leq k \\leq \\frac{5}{8}$. Mà $k \\in \\mathbb{Z} \\Rightarrow k = 0 \\Rightarrow x = \\frac{3\\pi}{8}$"
  },
